sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Founder
  participant Orchestrator as Genesis Orchestrator
  participant Publishing as Publishing Department
  participant DB as Genesis Database
  participant Provider as Publishing Provider

  Orchestrator->>Publishing: Send approved marketing pack
  Publishing->>DB: Load product, creative, and marketing assets
  Publishing-->>Orchestrator: Return publishing package
  Orchestrator->>Founder: Request publishing approval
  Founder-->>Orchestrator: Approve manual publishing
  Orchestrator->>Provider: Prepare publishing handoff
  Orchestrator->>DB: Store publishing status
